nyo e lekanang le barrier\'s HP. \n- {@green} Reflect{@DEFAULT}: Fumana feela 80% ea tšenyo ho tsoa ho sera, \'me u khutlisetse 20% ho mohlaseli. \n- {@green} Immune{@DEFAULT}: Tšireletso ea \'mele ho litlamorao tsohle tse kotsi. Litlamorao tse kotsi tsa hajoale ha li tlosoe. \n- {@green} HP Absorption{@DEFAULT}: Fumana 10% ea ts\'enyehelo e entsoeng ho sera joalo ka HP.',
